Product block Steps    Step Description Expected result     Go to BO -&gt; Orders -&gt; View last Order page The Order details page is displayed   Click on &ldquo;Delete&rdquo; button to remove the product and confirm the deletion An alert &ldquo;The product was successfully removed.&rdquo; is displayed and number products = 0   Click on Add a product The addProductTableRow is displayed   Search for standard simple product and click on it The &ldquo;Stock location&rdquo; value is correct and the &ldquo;Available&rdquo; quantity is correct   Click on &ldquo;Add&rdquo; A green alert &ldquo;The product was successfully added.&rdquo; is displayed and the new product is displayed in the list   Click on &ldquo;Add product&rdquo;, search the same product and click on &ldquo;Add&rdquo; A red alert &ldquo;Error! This product is already in your order, please edit the quantity instead.&rdquo; is displayed and the product cannot be added again   Click on the &ldquo;Cancel&rdquo; button The addProductTableRow is not displayed   Click on Add a product The addProductTableRow is displayed   Search for standard product with combinations and click on it The &ldquo;Stock location&rdquo; value is correct and the &ldquo;Available&rdquo; quantity is correct   Click on &ldquo;Add&rdquo; A green alert &ldquo;The product was successfully added.&rdquo; is displayed and the new product is displayed in the list   Click on Add a product The addProductTableRow is displayed   Search for virtual product and click on it The &ldquo;Stock location&rdquo; value is correct and the &ldquo;Available&rdquo; quantity is correct   Click on &ldquo;Add&rdquo; A green alert &ldquo;The product was successfully added.&rdquo; is displayed and the new product is displayed in the list   Click on Add a product The addProductTableRow is displayed   Search for pack product and click on it The &ldquo;Stock location&rdquo; value is correct and the &ldquo;Available&rdquo; quantity is correct   Click on &ldquo;Add&rdquo; A red alert &ldquo;{color:#FF0000}Error!{color}
{color:#FF0000}Minimum quantity of &ldquo;2&rdquo; must be added{color}&rdquo; is displayed   Increase quantity = minimal quantity The quantity is changed   Click on &ldquo;Add&rdquo; 1. A green alert &ldquo;The product was successfully added.&rdquo; is displayed and the new product is displayed in the list
2. The name is correct, the base price is correct, the quantity is correct, the Available is ok and the total is ok   Click on Add a product The addProductTableRow is displayed   Search for customized product (demo_14) and click on it The &ldquo;Stock location&rdquo; value is correct and the &ldquo;Available&rdquo; quantity is correct   Click on &ldquo;Add&rdquo; A green alert &ldquo;The product was successfully added.&rdquo; is displayed and the new product is displayed in the list   Click on Add a product The addProductTableRow is displayed   Search for an out of stock allowed product and click on it The &ldquo;Stock location&rdquo; value is correct and the &ldquo;Available&rdquo; quantity is correct   Click on &ldquo;Add&rdquo; A green alert &ldquo;The product was successfully added.&rdquo; is displayed and the new product is displayed in the list   Click on Add a product The addProductTableRow is displayed   Search for an out of stock not allowed product and click on it The &ldquo;Stock location&rdquo; value is correct, the &ldquo;Available&rdquo; quantity is correct and the &ldquo;Add&rdquo; button is disabled   Increase the quantity The &ldquo;Add&rdquo; button is still disabled   Click on &ldquo;Cancel&rdquo; button The addProductTableRow is not displayed   Click on Add a product The addProductTableRow is displayed   Search for a product with a specific price and click on it The base price and the total are correct   Click on Add a product The addProductTableRow is displayed   Search for a product with ecotax and click on it The base price and the total are correct   Click on Add a product The addProductTableRow is displayed   Search for a product with cart rule and click on it The base price and the total are correct Check that the discount line is well added   Click on &ldquo;Edit&rdquo; of the first product in the list The &ldquo;editProductRow&rdquo; is displayed   Edit the quantity, click on &ldquo;Save&rdquo; and confirm the modification The Quantity is correct   Click on &ldquo;Edit&rdquo; of the first product in the list The &ldquo;editProductRow&rdquo; is displayed   Edit the price, click on &ldquo;Save&rdquo; and confirm the modification The base price is correct and the total is correct   Click on Add&quot; A green alert &ldquo;The product was successfully added.&rdquo; is displayed and the new product is displayed in the list   Add 3 differents products to have more 8 products in the list The number of products in the list is correct   Click on &ldquo;Display with items&rdquo; = 8 and click on &ldquo;Next&rdquo; The pagiation number is equal to 2   Click on &ldquo;Previous&rdquo; The pagination number is equal to 1   Click on &ldquo;Display with items&rdquo; = 20 The pagiation doesn&rsquo;t exit: the Next button is not visible   Click on &ldquo;Display with items&rdquo; = 8 The pagiation is displayed &amp; the New button is visible

Generate Credit Slips By Date Steps    Step Description Expected result     Go to BO &gt; Orders &gt; &ldquo;Orders&rdquo; page Orders list is displayed successfully   Change the order status to &ldquo;Shipped&rdquo; The order status is updated successfully
The invoice is created successfully   Add a partial refund product the credit slip document is created successfully   Go to Orders &gt; &ldquo;Credit slips&rdquo; page Credit slips page is displayed successfully   Generate PDF file by date The file exists in the disk   Put a future date in From and To field An error message is displayed
&ldquo;No invoice has been found for this period.&rdquo;

Respond to message Steps    Step Description Expected result     In FO &gt; Go to Contact us Page &gt; Fill Fields &gt; Click Send Message &ldquo;Your message has been successfully sent to our team.&rdquo; appears   Go to BO &gt; Customer Service &gt; Customer Service &gt; In Customer Service Block &gt; Click View on latest thread Thread is displayed   Scroll to block &ldquo;Your answer to XXX&rdquo; &gt; Add a response &gt; Click Send The Thread is updated with your message
