Enable/Disable a currency Steps    Step Description Expected result     Go to BO &gt; International &gt; Localization &gt; Currencies &gt; Disable Euro currency Message &ldquo;You cannot disable the default currency&rdquo;
The currency is not disabled   Click &ldquo;Add new currency&rdquo; &gt; Choose USD &gt; Status &ldquo;No&rdquo; &gt; Save Message &ldquo;Successful creation.&quot;
Currency USD is disabled and displayed in the list   Enable USD from Currency list Message &ldquo;The status has been successfully updated.&quot;
USD is enabled   Go to Tab Localization &gt; Select Default currency = USD &gt; Save Message &ldquo;Update successful&rdquo;
USD is now the default currency   Go back to Tab Currencies &gt; Disable Euro Message &ldquo;The status has been successfully updated.&quot;
Currency Euro is disabled   Change your default currency to Euro and delete currency USD Message &ldquo;Successful deletion.&rdquo;
